Process called "translate_list_pattern" takes translator as Integer, pattern as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Translate list pattern to HIR

    Let hir_pattern be proc create_hir_node from HIR_PATTERN_LIST

    Let pattern_children be proc get_haskell_ast_children from Parser with pattern

    Note: Translate element patterns
    Let hir_elements be proc create_hir_list

