Process called "translate_tuple_pattern" takes translator as Integer, pattern as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Translate tuple pattern to HIR

    Let hir_pattern be proc create_hir_node from HIR_PATTERN_TUPLE

    Let pattern_children be proc get_haskell_ast_children from Parser with pattern

